titles.title: Electing members to the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 3/14/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Elects specified Members to the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.
